National Pulse Editor-in-Chief Raheem Kassam on Ukraine: How we got here and how it ends. Dems talk inflation, prove they know nothing about business. Libs distort Florida's Parental Rights in Education Bill, relentlessly push transgender agenda. Looking for levity in serious times. Washington Commanders trade for Carson Wentz, epidemic of stupidity in Washington, D.C. Book lovers C&B (and co-nerds as they lovingly referred to each other during the show) chat more about books. Giant spiders invade East Coast.
